  "texts": [
    "Toolkits and technical solutions, such as open-source repositories of ethically compliant technology solutions or ethics best practices for coding, can enable individual innovators to integrate ethics into their work.",
    "Self-reflection.",
    "Self-reflection by innovators is seen as a major catalyst to achieve values-driven innovation.",
    "Innovators, both at the individual and organization level, review the impact and purpose of an innovation at the outset, and throughout the development and implementation phases.",
    "As a senior pharmaceutical executive stressed, innovators should ask themselves whether an innovation delivers real utility to patients and end-users and whether they have integrated an ethical perspective on core issues such as privacy, autonomy, or justice."
